---
import imgPartner from "@images/parner-flight-training-finance-logo.webp"

import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import imgFinancing from "../../assets/images/cfi-with-student-at-blue-skies-above.webp";
---
<section class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-2 justify-center py-10 ">
  <div class="" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay={500}>
    <Image
      class="w-full rounded-lg"
      src={imgFinancing}
      alt=""
      format={"avif"}
    />
  </div>
  <div class="max-w-3xl flex flex-col py-10 px-5">
    <h2 class="text-5xl font-header uppercase font-semibold text-picton-blue-700 dark:text-picton-blue-400">Financing Your Flight Training</h2>
    <h3 class="text-2xl text-gray-800 dark:text-picton-blue-500 py-5">Accessible Financing Solutions for Your Pilot Training</h3>
    <p class="text-lg  text-gray-700 dark:text-white ">Our mission is to provide flexible solutions that fit your financial situation, allowing you to pursue your aviation dreams without the added stress of financial constraints.</p>
    <p class="text-lg  text-gray-700 dark:text-white pt-5">
      Whether you’re looking for personalized financing solutions, flexible payment plans, or transparent terms, our partnership with Flight Training Finance ensures you have access to competitive rates and terms. Our user-friendly application process and supportive financial aid advisors make it easier for you to secure the necessary funds for your flight training.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg  text-gray-700 dark:text-white  pt-5">
      We also offer scholarships and grants for eligible students, providing additional opportunities to support your aviation education. Our financial aid advisors are here to guide you through every step, helping you explore all available options so you can confidently take the first step towards your aviation career.
    </p>
    <p class="text-lg  text-gray-700 dark:text-white  pt-5">
      Don't let financial barriers hold you back. Get in touch with us today to learn more about our financing options and start your journey to becoming a pilot with Blue Skies Above and Flight Training Finance.
    </p>
    <a class="btn-primary w-fit mt-10 text-lg" href="/pricing">View Pricing for Our Training Packages</a>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="flex text-lg flex-col items-center ">
  <div class="max-w-7xl flex flex-col items-center bg-white rounded-lg p-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col-reverse lg:flex-row items-center w-full justify-around py-10 gap-10">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-5xl text-balance font-header font-semibold text-center uppercase">
          Finance with Flight Training Finance LLC
        </h2>
        <h3 class="pt-3 text-2xl text-center">
          Don’t let finances be the limiting factor
        </h3>
      </div>
      <Image
        class="h-12 sm:h-16 md:h-20"
        src={imgPartner}
        alt="Flight Training Finance logo"
        format={"webp"}
      />
    </div>
    <div class="tracking-wider">
      <p class="pt-5">
        Embarking on your journey to becoming a pilot is an exciting endeavor, and at Blue Skies Above, we understand the importance of making flight training accessible to everyone. That's why we've partnered with Flight Training Finance to offer tailored financing solutions designed to support your flight goals.
      </p>
      <p class="pt-5 font-semibold text-xl">
        Why Choose Flight Training Finance?
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-10 pt-5">
        <li>
          <strong>Personalized Solutions:</strong> We believe that every
          student's journey is unique. With Flight Training Finance, you'll
          have access to financing options customized to your individual
          needs and circumstances.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Guidance Every Step of the Way:</strong> Our user-friendly
          Flight Training Finance Application walks you through the process,
          ensuring clarity and simplicity as you apply for financing.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Flexible Payment Plans:</strong> Whether you're looking to
          spread out your payments or make a larger down payment, our Yellow
          Sheet calculation tool allows you to explore different payment
          scenarios, empowering you to find a plan that fits your budget.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Transparent Terms:</strong> Rest assured that with the
          Retail Installment Contract, you'll have a clear understanding of
          the terms of your financing agreement, providing peace of mind as
          you pursue your dreams.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="pt-5">
        If you are interested in getting started, please click
        <a href="https://www.flighttrainingfinancellc.com/apply-for-financing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="hover:text-blue-800 hover:underline text-blue-600 font-semibold">
          here
        </a>
        to apply now.
      </p>
      <p class="pt-10 font-semibold text-xl">Partnering for Success</p>
      <p class="pt-5">
        Blue Skies Above and Flight Training Finance have come together to streamline the financing process, making flight training more accessible to aspiring pilots like you. Take the first step towards your aviation goals by exploring our financing options today.
      </p>
      <p class="pt-5">
        Don't let financial barriers hold you back from reaching new heights. Start your journey with Blue Skies Above and Flight Training Finance.
      </p>

